OL,3,CPrincess Charlotte smiles on holiday
OL,4,Cin new photo to mark 11th birthday
OL,6,FThe Prince and Princess of Wales have
OL,7,Fshared a new photo of their daughter
OL,8,FCharlotte walking in a field of
OL,9,Fdaisies as they mark her 11th birthday.
OL,11,FThe image, shot by photographer Matt
OL,12,FPorteous during the family's Easter
OL,13,Fbreak in Cornwall, shows Charlotte
OL,14,Fwearing a black and red striped jumper
OL,15,Fand blue denim jeans.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
