OL,3,CPrincess Charlotte smiles on holiday
OL,4,Cin new photo to mark 11th birthday
OL,6,FIt was posted on the Kensington Palace
OL,7,Fsocial media accounts with the
OL,8,Fmessage: "Wishing Charlotte a very
OL,9,Fhappy 11th birthday!"
OL,11,FCharlotte was born at 8.34am on May 2
OL,12,F2015 at St Mary's Hospital in
OL,13,FPaddington, weighing 8lb 3oz.
OL,15,FThe princess is sister to George, 12,
OL,16,Fand Louis, eight, and fourth in line
OL,17,Fto the throne.
