OL,3,CPrincess Charlotte smiles on holiday
OL,4,Cin new photo to mark 11th birthday
OL,6,FThe children all attend Lambrook
OL,7,FSchool, in Berkshire, close to the
OL,8,Ffamily's home in Windsor, where they
OL,9,Fwill stay until they turn 13.
OL,11,FGeorge is in his last year of the
OL,12,Fschool, and will turn 13 in July.
OL,14,FKate and William recently celebrated
OL,15,F15 years of marriage on April 29,
OL,16,Fsharing a family photo online to mark
OL,17,Fthe occasion.
