OL,3,CPrincess Charlotte smiles on holiday
OL,4,Cin new photo to mark 11th birthday
OL,6,FThe image, also shot by Porteous,
OL,7,Fshowed the prince and princess with
OL,8,Ftheir three children relaxing in the
OL,9,Fgrass during the Easter break.
OL,11,FOn Friday, the family also celebrated
OL,12,Ftheir second dog Otto's first birthday
OL,13,Fby posting a picture of the brown
OL,14,Fspaniel on social media.
OL,16,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,17,Fweekly podcast about the Royal Family,
OL,18,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,19,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson.
